WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.880
You can tell if a marriage will fail or not

00:00:02.881 --> 00:00:04.721
by the way a woman treats her man.

00:00:04.722 --> 00:00:05.801
Okay, hear me out.

00:00:05.802 --> 00:00:08.441
If a woman doesn't appreciate her man,

00:00:08.442 --> 00:00:10.801
doesn't support him, respect him,

00:00:10.802 --> 00:00:13.601
give him his flowers, and not literally,

00:00:13.602 --> 00:00:16.481
but figuratively, then that marriage will fail.

00:00:16.482 --> 00:00:18.761
Or worse, it'll leave the guy cheating on her.

00:00:18.762 --> 00:00:22.501
If a man does not feel appreciated and supported,

00:00:22.600 --> 00:00:25.740
that marriage will never, ever last.
